      "value": "<p><strong>Level 1</strong> Enchantment</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> 30 feet</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (a morsel of food)</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> 24 hours</p>\n\nTarget a Beast that you can see within range. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or have the Charmed|XPHB condition for the duration. If you or one of your allies deals damage to the target, the spells ends.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> You can target one additional Beast for each spell slot level above 1.</p>",
